transcript:

Executive: Um main kuch thoda sa main lead ek kaam karti hu dusri laga ke aapko call karti hu. Matlab aap call pe rahiye main change karti hu. Theek hai?
Customer: Aap aapko connect pe dikh raha hai screen dikh raha hai aapko share?
Executive: Aap connect hi rahiye main ek minute mein aa rahi hu bas lead change kar rahi hu theek hai?
Customer: Okay okay okay okay theek hai theek hai okay madam.
